SliTaz PiTFT Touchscreen
------------------------

SliTaz runs nicely on PiTFT! Here are some notes about cross compiling the
fbtft kernel driver and about customization. The default X session is
powered by sts.

Custom configs are in slitaz-arm/flavors/pitft


Adafruit Fork of FBTFT for use with Adafruit TS shield
------------------------------------------------------
https://github.com/adafruit/adafruit-rpi-fbtft/


Adafruit guides
---------------
https://learn.adafruit.com/adafruit-pitft-28-inch-resistive-touchscreen-display-raspberry-pi

